A simple C++ airline reservation system that manages passenger bookings, cancellations, searches, and reservation updates using a linked-list structure. The program runs through a menu-driven interface for easy interaction.

Features
Add new reservations
Cancel reservations
Search for passengers
Modify existing bookings
View full passenger list
Generate reservation reports

File Structure
airlines.h      → class & struct definitions  
airlines.cpp    → function implementations  
main.cpp        → menu + program entry  
How to Run

Compile all files:

g++ main.cpp airlines.cpp -o airline_app

Run the program:

./airline_app
Requirements
GCC or any C++ compiler
VS Code or any C++-compatible IDE
